# Adding a new design (Design Marketplace)

- **Create folder**: `src/app/designs/<design-slug>/` (kebab-case)
- **Slug must match**: `preview.tsx` â†’ `metadata.id`
- **Required files**:
  - `guidelines.md`: the design system spec
  - `layout.tsx`: reads `guidelines.md` and wraps with `DesignPageLayout`
  - `page.tsx`: full showcase page (real UI built from the guidelines)
  - `preview.tsx`: exports `metadata` + `PreviewComponent` (homepage card)

## Contracts to follow

- `preview.tsx` exports:
  - `export const metadata = { id, name, description, tags }`
  - `export function PreviewComponent() { ... }`
- `layout.tsx`:
  - Read markdown from: `path.join(process.cwd(), 'src/app/designs/<slug>/guidelines.md')`
  - Render: `<DesignPageLayout title="<Design Name>" markdown={markdown}>{children}</DesignPageLayout>`

## When done

- Register the design in `src/app/page.tsx` by importing `metadata` + `PreviewComponent` and appending to the `designs` array.
